- What you doing?
- I'm sorry. Just peeking.

558
01:13:58,806 --> 01:14:01,934
- How do I look?
- You look better.

559
01:14:02,101 --> 01:14:05,145
- Just better?
- Well...

560
01:14:05,312 --> 01:14:06,563
...you look beautiful.

561
01:14:10,192 --> 01:14:11,860
