577
01:15:02,911 --> 01:15:06,123
This is my savior, J.F. Sebastian.

578
01:15:06,290 --> 01:15:07,791
Sebastian.

579
01:15:08,459 --> 01:15:11,170
I like a man that stays put.

580
01:15:12,713 --> 01:15:16,049
