646
01:21:36,971 --> 01:21:38,723
Queen...

647
01:21:40,350 --> 01:21:42,393
...bishop six.

648
01:21:47,482 --> 01:21:49,859
<i>Knight...</i>

649
01:21:50,026 --> 01:21:52,278
